We and our neighbors are
shielded against the neutrons

39:31.202 --> 39:33.481
by three feet of concrete.

39:33.505 --> 39:36.951
It's also shielded
by this copper mesh

39:36.975 --> 39:39.987
that radio waves
can't get through.

